From: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
Date: Mon, 2 Jun 2025 14:49:13 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 13/13] FROMLIST: Fix build with GCC >= 14

Add additional system header #include directives for more
function prototypes.  This avoids implicit function declarations
and build failures with future compilers.

Signed-off-by: Florian Weimer <fweimer@redhat.com>

Link: https://sourceforge.net/p/aa-project/bugs/10/#36b9
Signed-off-by: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
---
 src/aafire.c     | 1 +
 src/aainfo.c     | 1 +
 src/aakbdreg.c   | 1 +
 src/aalib.c      | 1 +
 src/aalinuxkbd.c | 1 +
 src/aamoureg.c   | 1 +
 src/aaregist.c   | 1 +
 src/aasavefont.c | 1 +
 src/aatest.c     | 2 ++
 src/aaxkbd.c     | 1 +
 10 files changed, 11 insertions(+)

diff --git a/src/aafire.c b/src/aafire.c
index 4f36149..a59b5c5 100644
--- a/src/aafire.c
+++ b/src/aafire.c
@@ -1,4 +1,5 @@
 #include <stdio.h>
+#include <stdlib.h>
 #include "aalib.h"
 
 #define XSIZ aa_imgwidth(context)
